      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0623P0-03874'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0623P0_20010315_GCR_183' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 114 [<span class="italic">Premises with resident landlord</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0623P0-03875'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0623P0_20010315_GCR_184' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
