      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0623P0-03995'>
        <a name='S5LV0623P0_20010315_GCR_304'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-charles-lyell' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0623P0_20010315_GCR_304' title='Link to this speech by Mr Charles Lyell' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-charles-lyell" title="Mr Charles Lyell">The Deputy Chairman of Committees</a></cite>
