        Clause 124 [<span class="italic">Disregard of marriage value in case of very long leases</span>]:
      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_240gc' title='Col. 240GC &mdash; HL Deb 15 March 2001 vol 623 c240GC' name='column_240gc' href='#column_240gc' rel='bookmark'>240GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0623P0-04013'>
